{"tid":2093620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"發起洪災募捐 中國紅會僅籌二千元","createTime":"2020-07-04T03:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:44:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4f97a5d9828d0bf66c9413b1a6c74837e1fae3","tid":2093620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200704/FYDQURUWBFTQ5ULBHDPELBQNRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200704%2FFYDQURUWBFTQ5ULBHDPELBQNRA%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=de0e05f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200704%2FFYDQURUWBFTQ5ULBHDPELBQNRA%2F&h=1e51dcca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200704/FYDQURUWBFTQ5ULBHDPELBQNRA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n發起洪災募捐 中國紅會僅籌二千元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/alLDBGRdLRG32w4UMBvQMviEsqM=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CFLNZMLYWUIBNFTXXJS5EYTCYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FalLDBGRdLRG32w4UMBvQMviEsqM%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCFLNZMLYWUIBNFTXXJS5EYTCYU.jpg&h=b79797b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重慶綦江洪過境，靠江邊的民居被淹。<br />\n<br />\n中國自6月以來近26個省市遭遇水災，1,938萬人受影響。中國紅十字會在上月12日發起網上募捐賑災，至7月2日共20日只籌得2,000元（約2,195港元），與目標60萬（約65萬港元）金額只是九牛一毛。官方解釋水災關注度不足，但網民認為是因中國紅十字會臭名遠播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n文章已經被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民歸咎臭名遠播<br />\n<br />\n不少網民不同意官方解釋，有網民稱：「想到武漢的捐款，想到當年汶川地震的捐贈物資，我沒法兒捐」、「畢竟是和世界其他紅十字會性質都不一樣的紅十字會」。中國紅十字會與國際紅十字會並無聯繫，中國紅十字會過往醜聞多多，郭美美案令人質疑慈款被個人挪用炫富，汶川地震亦揭出中國紅十字會收集的物資囤積，放到腐爛仍未交到所需人士。今年的武漢肺炎，中國紅十字會亦屢被指摘物資遭高層挪用。<br />\n<br />\n中國慈善家/微博"},{"pid":"9d1567e6cc025562e529b333fe48570e22f43b5d","tid":2093620,"uid":2267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"支那人：你死你事，關我撚事"},{"pid":"95dc0ecaea1d6afaec9aa94db264c39ac9cef2a3","tid":2093620,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a>"},{"pid":"1c50c2d887f621ca56ad70f5d17f61b0e1fa8c85","tid":2093620,"uid":76364,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"仲有人捐兩千先好野"},{"pid":"1d47cde253f7f2b16b07726f8119bdd96c078a48","tid":2093620,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"血濃於水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2384fa0065ba42ac22f4f3e23142746538ef711b","tid":2093620,"uid":52693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"見圖飲水"},{"pid":"34583cb382ad1d90fcbc119c51fd01c2d0e00278","tid":2093620,"uid":90315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，香港政府： 爭幾多，我貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98501999eccb78e026d8297ba0f2e387a7c562cc","tid":2093620,"uid":26385,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:41:05.000Z","msg":"連中國人自己都知咩事<br />\n偏偏有啲香港人仲係on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3cf496ff892b75f07aa864477be5ee6e399a54","tid":2093620,"uid":27146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"支那人：新聞都無講，鬼知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa594ba3c2daf12f5b4191205741dfa72078c0e","tid":2093620,"uid":91648,"like":0